  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Automated mitosis detection was used to assess mitotic counts through three methods: mitotic count per tumor area (MCT), mitotic index (MI), and mitotic activity index (MAI).",
    "These methods were then compared with the Nottingham grading system, Ki67 scores, clinicopathologic parameters, and patient outcomes.",
    "AI-based scores from all three methods (MCT, MI, and MAI) showed significant correlations with clinicopathologic characteristics and patient survival (P < 0.001) [4].",
    "A thesis regarding breast screening-AI framework integrating multimodal imaging and AI for image analysis revealed enhanced diagnostic efficiency, reduced cognitive workload, and improved clinician satisfaction.",
    "It highlighted the transformative impact of intelligent agents in supporting clinical workflows and decision-making."
  ],
